==English==
===Pronoun===
'''what's-his-name'''

# A person or entity whose [[name]] one does not [[remember]] but that is known to the person to which one is speaking.
# A person or entity whose [[name]] one does not want to [[mention]] but that is known to the person to which one is speaking.

==== Quotations ====

*'''1885''' — [[w:Gilbert and Sullivan|Gilbert & Sullivan]], ''[[s:The_Mikado|The Mikado]]''
*:And 'St—'st—'st and '''What's-his-name''', and also You-know-who—
*:The task of filling up the blanks I'd rather leave to you.

